[
    {
        "source_sentence": "解深密經卷第五",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大唐三藏法師玄奘奉　詔譯",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "8 如來成所作事品(五)如來成所作事品第八",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，曼殊室利菩薩摩訶薩請問佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b14_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如佛所說如來法身，如來法身有何等相？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告曼殊室利菩薩曰：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b16_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b16_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若於諸地波羅蜜多，善修出離，轉依成滿，是名如來法身之相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知此相，二因緣故不可思議：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b18_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無戲論故，無所為故。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b19_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而諸眾生計著戲論，有所為故。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聲聞、獨覺所得轉依，名法身不？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b21_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不名法身。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b22_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當名何身？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b22_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b22_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "名解脫身。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由解脫身故，說一切聲聞、獨覺與諸如來平等平等；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b24_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由法身故，說有差別。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來法身有差別故，無量功德最勝差別，算數譬喻所不能及。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b26_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」曼殊室利菩薩復白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b26_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我當云何應知如來生起之相？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b27_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告曼殊室利菩薩曰：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b28_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切如來化身作業，如世界起一切種類；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708b29_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來功德眾所莊嚴，住持為相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知化身相有生起，法身之相無有生起。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c02_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」曼殊室利菩薩復白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c02_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何應知示現化身方便善巧？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告曼殊室利菩薩曰：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c04_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "遍於一切三千大千佛國土中，或眾推許增上王家，或眾推許大福田家，同時入胎、誕生、長大、受欲、出家、示行苦行、捨苦行已成等正覺，次第示現。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c07_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是名如來示現化身方便善巧。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」曼殊室利菩薩復白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c09_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "凡有幾種，一切如來身所住持言音差別？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c10_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由此言音所化有情，未成熟者令其成熟，已成熟者緣此為境速得解脫？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c11_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告曼殊室利菩薩曰：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c12_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c12_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來言音略有三種：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、契經；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c13_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、調伏；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c13_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、本母。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c13_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何契經？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何調伏？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c14_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何本母？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c14_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」「曼殊室利！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c14_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若於是處，我依攝事顯示諸法，是名契經。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c15_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂依四事，或依九事，或復依於二十九事。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c16_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「云何四事？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c17_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、聽聞事；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、歸趣事；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c17_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、修學事；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、菩提事。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c18_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「云何九事？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、施設有情事；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、彼所受用事；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c19_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、彼生起事；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c19_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、彼生已住事；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、彼染淨事；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c20_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、彼差別事；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c20_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、能宣說事；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c21_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、所宣說事；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、諸眾會事。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c21_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「云何名為二十九事？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c22_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂依雜染品有：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c22_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "攝諸行事，彼次第隨轉事，即於是中作補特伽羅想已，於當來世流轉因事，作是想已，於當來世流轉因事。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c25_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依清淨品有：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c25_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "繫念於所緣事，即於是中勤精進事，心安住事，現法樂住事，超一切苦緣方便事，彼遍知事。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此復三種：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0708c28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "顛倒遍知所依處故，依有情想外有情中邪行遍知所依處故，內離增上慢遍知所依處故。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a01_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "修依處事，作證事，修習事，令彼堅固事，彼行相事，彼所緣事，已斷未斷觀察善巧事，彼散亂事，彼不散亂事，不散亂依處事，不棄修習劬勞加行事，修習勝利事，彼堅牢事，攝聖行事，攝聖行眷屬事，通達真實事，證得涅槃事，於善說法毘奈耶中世間正見超昇一切外道所得正見頂事，及即於此不修退事，於善說法毘奈耶中不修習故，說名為退，非見過失，故名為退。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「曼殊室利！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a09_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若於是處，我依聲聞及諸菩薩，顯示別解脫及別解脫相應之法，是名調伏。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a11_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a11_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩別解脫，幾相所攝？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a12_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知七相：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a12_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、宣說受軌則事故；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a13_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、宣說隨順他勝事故；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a13_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、宣說隨順毀犯事故；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a14_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、宣說有犯自性故；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、宣說無犯自性故；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a15_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、宣說出所犯故；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、宣說捨律儀故。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「曼殊室利！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a17_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若於是處，我以十一種相決了分別顯示諸法，是名本母。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a18_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等名為十一種相？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、世俗相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a19_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、勝義相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a19_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、菩提分法所緣相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、行相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a20_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、自性相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a20_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、彼果相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a20_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、彼領受開示相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a21_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、彼障礙法相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a21_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者、彼隨順法相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十者、彼過患相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十一者、彼勝利相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世俗相者，當知三種：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a23_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、宣說補特伽羅故；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、宣說遍計所執自性故；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a24_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、宣說諸法作用事業故。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a25_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "勝義相者，當知宣說七種真如故。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a26_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩提分法所緣相者，當知宣說遍一切種所知事故。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a27_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「行相者，當知宣說八行觀故。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何名為八行觀耶？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a28_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、諦實故；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、安住故；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a29_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、過失故；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a29_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、功德故；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709a29_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、理趣故；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b01_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、流轉故；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b01_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、道理故；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b01_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、總別故。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「諦實者，謂諸法真如。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b02_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「安住者，謂或安立補特伽羅，或復安立諸法遍計所執自性，或復安立一向、分別、反問、置記，或復安立隱密、顯了、記別、差別。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b05_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "過失者，謂我宣說諸雜染法，有無量門差別過患。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b06_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「功德者，謂我宣說諸清淨法，有無量門差別勝利。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b07_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「理趣者，當知六種：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、真義理趣；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b08_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、證得理趣；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b08_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、教導理趣；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、遠離二邊理趣；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b09_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、不可思議理趣；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b10_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、意趣理趣。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b10_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「流轉者，所謂三世三有為相，及四種緣。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b11_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「道理者，當知四種：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b11_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、觀待道理；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b12_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、作用道理；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b12_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、證成道理；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b12_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、法爾道理。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b13_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀待道理者，謂若因若緣，能生諸行，及起隨說，如是名為觀待道理。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b14_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作用道理者，謂若因若緣，能得諸法，或能成辦，或復生已作諸業用，如是名為作用道理。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b16_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "證成道理者，謂若因若緣，能令所立、所說、所標、義得成立，令正覺悟，如是名為證成道理。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b18_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又此道理略有二種：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b19_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、清淨；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b19_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者不清淨。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b19_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由五種相名為清淨，由七種相名不清淨。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「云何由五種相名為清淨？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b22_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、現見所得相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b22_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、依止現見所得相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b23_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、自類譬喻所引相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、圓成實相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b24_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、善清淨言教相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b24_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「現見所得相者，謂一切行皆無常性，一切行皆是苦性，一切法皆無我性，此為世間現量所得。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b26_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是等類，是名現見所得相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「依止現見所得相者，謂一切行皆剎那性，他世有性，淨不淨業無失壞性。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709b29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由彼能依麁無常性，現可得故。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由諸有情種種差別，依種種業現可得故，由諸有情若樂若苦，淨不淨業以為依止，現可得故。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c03_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由此因緣，於不現見可為比度。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是等類，是名依止現見所得相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c04_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「自類譬喻所引相者，謂於內外諸行聚中，引諸世間共所了知所得生死以為譬喻，引諸世間共所了知所得生等種種苦相以為譬喻，引諸世間共所了知所得不自在相以為譬喻，又復於外引諸世間共所了知所得衰盛以為譬喻。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是等類，當知是名自類譬喻所引相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c11_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「圓成實相者，謂即如是現見所得相，若依止現見所得相，若自類譬喻所得相，於所成立，決定能成，當知是名圓成實相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c13_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善清淨言教相者，謂一切智者之所宣說，如言涅槃究竟寂靜，如是等類，當知是名善清淨言教相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c16_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c16_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故由此五種相故，名善觀察清淨道理，由清淨故，應可修習。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c17_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」曼殊室利菩薩復白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c18_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c18_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切智相者，當知有幾種？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告曼殊室利菩薩曰：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c19_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c19_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "略有五種：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、若有出現世間一切智聲，無不普聞；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、成就三十二種大丈夫相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c21_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、具足十力，能斷一切眾生一切疑惑；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c22_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、具足四無所畏宣說正法，不為一切他論所伏，而能摧伏一切邪論；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c24_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、於善說法、毘奈耶中，八支聖道、四沙門等，皆現可得。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c25_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是生故，相故，斷疑網故，非他所伏能伏他故，聖道、沙門現可得故，如是五種，當知名為一切智相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c28_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c28_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是證成道理，由現量故、由比量故、由聖教量故。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0709c29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由五種相，名為清淨。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「云何由七種相名不清淨？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a02_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、此餘同類可得相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、此餘異類可得相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、一切同類可得相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、一切異類可得相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a04_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、異類譬喻所得相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a05_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、非圓成實相；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a05_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、非善清淨言教相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若一切法意識所識性，是名一切同類可得相，若一切法相性業法因果異相，由隨如是一一異相，決定展轉各各異相，是名一切異類可得相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a09_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a09_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若於此餘同類可得相，及譬喻中有一切異類相者，由此因緣，於所成立非決定故，是名非圓成實相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又於此餘異類可得相，及譬喻中有一切同類相者，由此因緣，於所成立不決定故，亦名非圓成實相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a14_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "非圓成實故，非善觀察清淨道理，不清淨故，不應修習。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a15_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若異類譬喻所引相，若非善清淨言教相，當知體性皆不清淨。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「法爾道理者，謂如來出世，若不出世，法性，安住、法住，法界，是名法爾道理。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a18_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「總別者，謂先總說一句法已，後後諸句差別分別究竟顯了。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「自性相者，謂我所說有行有緣，所有能取菩提分法，謂念住等，如是名為彼自性相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a22_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼果相者，謂若世間若出世間，諸煩惱斷，及所引發世出世間諸果功德，如是名為得彼果相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼領受開示相者，謂即於彼，以解脫智而領受之，及廣為他宣說開示，如是名為彼領受開示相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a27_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼障礙法相者，謂即於修菩提分法，能隨障礙諸染污法，是名彼障礙法相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710a29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼隨順法相者，謂即於彼多所作法，是名彼隨順法相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼過患相者，當知即彼諸障礙法所有過失，是名彼過患相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b02_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼勝利相者，當知即彼諸隨順法所有功德，是名彼勝利相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」曼殊室利菩薩復白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b05_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唯願世尊為諸菩薩略說契經、調伏、本母、不共外道陀羅尼義，由此不共陀羅尼義，令諸菩薩得入如來所說諸法甚深密意。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b08_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告曼殊室利菩薩曰：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b09_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今諦聽，吾當為汝略說不共陀羅尼義，令諸菩薩，於我所說密意言詞能善悟入。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b11_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若雜染法、若清淨法，我說一切皆無作用，亦都無有補特伽羅，以一切種離所為故。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b13_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "非雜染法先染後淨，非清淨法後淨先染，凡夫異生，於麁重身，執著諸法、補特伽羅自性差別，隨眠妄見以為緣故，計我我所；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由此妄見，謂我見、我聞、我嗅、我甞、我觸、我知、我食、我作、我染、我淨，如是等類邪加行轉。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b18_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有如實知如是者，便能永斷麁重之身，獲得一切煩惱不住，最極清淨，離諸戲論，無為依止，無有加行。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b20_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是名略說不共陀羅尼義。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊欲重宣此義，而說頌曰：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b22_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「一切雜染清淨法，　　皆無作用數取趣。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b23_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由我宣說離所為，　　染污清淨非先後。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於麁重身隨眠見，　　為緣計我及我所；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b25_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由此妄謂我見等，　　我食我為我染淨。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b26_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若如實知如是者，　　乃能永斷麁重身，",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "得無染淨無戲論，　　無為依止無加行。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b28_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，曼殊室利菩薩摩訶薩復白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b29_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710b29_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何應知諸如來心生起之相？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c01_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告曼殊室利菩薩曰：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c02_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夫如來者，非心意識生起所顯，然諸如來有無加行心法生起，當知此事猶如變化。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」曼殊室利菩薩復白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c04_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若諸如來法身，遠離一切加行；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "既無加行，云何而有心法生起？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c06_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告曼殊室利菩薩曰：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c06_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "先所修習方便般若加行力故，有心生起。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如正入無心睡眠，非於覺悟而作加行，由先所作加行勢力而復覺悟。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如正在滅盡定中，非於起定而作加行，由先所作加行勢力，還從定起。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c11_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如從睡眠及滅盡定心更生起，如是如來由先修習方便般若加行力故，當知復有心法生起。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」曼殊室利菩薩復白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c14_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來化身，當言有心為無心耶？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c15_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告曼殊室利菩薩曰：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "非是有心，亦非無心。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c16_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c16_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無自依心故，有依他心故。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c17_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」曼殊室利菩薩復白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來所行，如來境界，此之二種，有何差別？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告曼殊室利菩薩曰：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c19_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c19_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來所行，謂一切種，如來共有不可思議無量功德，眾所莊嚴清淨佛土。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c21_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來境界，謂一切種，五界差別。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為五？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、有情界；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c22_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、世界；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c23_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、法界；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c23_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、調伏界；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c23_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、調伏方便界。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是名為二種差別。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c24_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」曼殊室利菩薩復白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c25_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c25_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來成等正覺、轉正法輪、入大涅槃，如是三種，當知何相？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c26_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告曼殊室利菩薩曰：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c27_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c27_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知此三皆無二相。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂非成等正覺、非不成等正覺；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c28_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "非轉正法輪、非不轉正法輪；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0710c29_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "非入大涅槃、非不入大涅槃。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a01_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a01_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來法身究竟淨故，如來化身常示現故。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a02_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」曼殊室利菩薩復白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a02_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸有情類，但於化身見聞奉事生諸功德，如來於彼有何因緣？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a04_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告曼殊室利菩薩曰：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來是彼增上所緣之因緣故。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a05_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又彼化身，是如來力所住持故。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a06_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」曼殊室利菩薩復白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a07_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a07_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "等無加行，何因緣故如來法身，為諸有情放大智光，及出無量化身影像？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聲聞、獨覺解脫之身，無如是事？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告曼殊室利菩薩曰：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a10_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a10_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如等無加行，從日、月輪水火二種頗胝迦寶放大光明，非餘水火頗胝迦寶，謂大威德有情所住持故，諸有情業增上力故。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a13_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如從彼善工業者之所雕飾，末尼寶珠出印文像，不從所餘不雕飾者。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是緣於無量法界方便般若，極善修習磨瑩，集成如來法身，從是能放大智光明及出種種化身影像，非唯從彼解脫之身，有如斯事。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a18_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」曼殊室利菩薩復白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a18_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如世尊說：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a19_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『如來、菩薩威德住持，令諸眾生於欲界中，生剎帝利、婆羅門等大富貴家，人身財寶無不圓滿，或欲界天、色、無色界，一切身財圓滿可得。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a22_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此中有何密意？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a22_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告曼殊室利菩薩曰：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a23_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a23_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來、菩薩威德住持，若道若行，於一切處，能令眾生獲得身財皆圓滿者，即隨所應，為彼宣說此道此行。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有能於此道此行正修行者，於一切處所獲身財無不圓滿。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711a27_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有眾生於此道行違背輕毀，又於我所起損惱心及瞋恚心，命終已後，於一切處所得身財無不下劣。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "曼殊室利！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b01_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由是因緣，當知如來及諸菩薩威德住持，非但能令身財圓滿，如來、菩薩住持威德，亦令眾生身財下劣。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」曼殊室利菩薩復白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b04_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸穢土中，何事易得？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b04_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何事難得？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b05_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸淨土中，何事易得？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何事難得？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b05_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告曼殊室利菩薩曰：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b06_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b06_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸穢土中，八事易得，二事難得。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等名為八事易得？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b07_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、外道；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者、有苦眾生；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者、種姓家世興衰差別；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者、行諸惡行；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者、毀犯尸羅；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者、惡趣；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者、下乘；",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b10_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者、下劣意樂加行菩薩。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b10_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等名為二事難得？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b11_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者、增上意樂加行菩薩之所遊集，二者、如來出現于世。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b12_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "曼殊室利！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b12_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸淨土中與上相違，當知八事甚為難得，二事易得。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，曼殊室利菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b15_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b15_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於此解深密法門中，此名何教？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b16_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我當云何奉持？",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b16_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告曼殊室利菩薩曰：",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b17_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此名如來成所作事了義之教，於此如來成所作事了義之教，汝當奉持。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b19_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」說是如來成所作事了義教時，於大會中有七十五千菩薩摩訶薩，皆得圓滿法身證覺。",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b21_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "解深密經卷第五",
        "from": "T16n0676_005:0711b22_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]